{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSPredicate","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSPredicate"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"predicate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use the style layer’s predicate to include only the features in the source"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer that satisfy a condition that you define. If the style layer initially"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"comes from the style, its predicate corresponds to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"filter"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property in the style JSON."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See the “"},{"type":"text","text":"Predicates and Expressions"},{"type":"text","text":"”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"guide for details about the predicate syntax supported by this class."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To filter the layer to include only the features whose "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"index"},{"type":"text","text":" attribute is 5"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"or 10 and whose ","type":"text"},{"code":"ele","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" attribute is at least 1,500, you could create an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSCompoundPredicate"},{"type":"text","text":" along these lines:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let layer = MLNLineStyleLayer(identifier: \"contour\", source: terrai